PrecisAppointment of Yves Dupras, of Île-des-Soeurs, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designation of the said Yves Dupras for the Quebec region, as established under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that he shall reside within 100 kilometres of the Quebec regional office.
Attachments
precis:
Appointment of Yves Dupras, of Île-des-Soeurs, Quebec, as a full-time
member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission
to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years;
designation of the said Yves Dupras for the Quebec region, as established
under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that he shall reside
within 100 kilometres of the Quebec regional office.
